INSERT INTO `Report` VALUES ('03d5257a-bc07-4622-90ca-7d2f8457069a','Aby Dash – Stock Fix & Order Update Report','\"\\\"<h1><strong>Aby Dash – Stock Fix &amp; Order Update Report</strong></h1><p><strong>Name: </strong>Ishimwe Serge</p><p><br></p><p>? <strong>Introduction</strong></p><p>Today, I completed important updates on the Aby Dash system focused on fixing stock-related issues and improving how client orders are managed. The goal was to ensure accurate stock tracking and make the ordering process smoother and more efficient.</p><p>✅ <strong>Key Tasks Completed</strong></p><p>? <strong>1. Fixed Stock Calculation Issues</strong></p><p>Identified and resolved inconsistencies in stock quantity updates.</p><p> Ensured that adding, removing, or modifying items correctly adjusts stock levels.</p><p> Improved the reliability of the stock management system for daily use.</p><p>? <strong>2. Added Logic to Attach New Items to Existing Client Orders</strong></p><p>Implemented a feature that checks if a client already has an active order.</p><p> If an order exists, new requested items are added to their current order instead of creating a new one.</p><p> Ensured the system merges items correctly and updates totals accurately.</p><p>? <strong>3. Backend &amp; UI Improvements</strong></p><p>Optimized order-handling logic for better performance.</p><p> Updated UI messages and flow to make actions clearer to staff.</p><p> Improved accuracy of order summaries and stock reflections on the dashboard.</p><p>? <strong>4. Responsiveness &amp; Testing</strong></p><p>Tested all updates across devices to ensure smooth usage.</p><p> Verified that order updates, stock changes, and UI responses are consistent across mobile, tablet, and desktop.</p><p>? <strong>Summary</strong></p><p>The Aby Dash system now offers:</p><p>? Accurate stock updates</p><p> ? Automatic merging of new items into existing client orders</p><p> ? Improved backend logic and UI clarity</p><p> ? Full responsiveness an